policy.
</P>
<P>
   (OPTIONAL MATERIAL FOLLOWS)
</P>
<P>
   Her tastes are traditional. Explainers are a staple of
newspapers and newsmagazines, of programs like ABC's ``Nightline''
and of correspondents like CNN's Jeff Greenfield. But they may not
