<P>
   NEW-SHERIFF (Los Angeles) _ Open doors symbolize the approach
Los Angeles County's new sheriff, Lee Baca, has taken toward his
job. ``I'm not . . . concerned,'' he said of his accessible office.
``Someone might try to come and shoot me, but I'll be wearing a
uniform and a gun _ and I'll probably shoot them first.'' By
Phillip W. Browne. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n''
