<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-14 20:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5152 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BIOPASS-SFCHRON-BIOPA     02-14 1311
